Metadata.Title: Take over the Yates empire
Metadata.Description: Don Yates has an incredible amount of money, power and connections. His lawyer, wife and security need to be eliminated in order to claim his empire. His bodyguards are not considered a target, merely an obstacle. The snipers however have been given your photo and need to be eliminated before escaping is possible. For this you shall use the speedboat. Everyone is cleared for elimination except your own lawyer called Diana Burnwood, who will make sure the empire falls into your hands. Good Luck.
